<br>
So, the Sullen Shamaness fell to her knees at the base of the Warrior Bard's unlit pyre. She laid the bracelet there by the flowers. She brought her ivory hands to her face craddling tears that stained her features. Her cries of mourning could be clearly heard, she laid down beside Gabrielle's body and began whispering in the Ancient Northren Langauge. She whispered cries of sadness til she could give out wrds of blessing. She prayed to the Mother Goddess before rising to her feet and sulking to Xena's side and resting her head on her friend's shoulder.<br>
