<br>
She took a stand at her half sisters side, those grey orbs turned to the Virgin Huntress.<br>
<br>
&quot;You have my deepest sympathy. She was a great, and true warrior.&quot; <p>_.- Goddess Athena, Goddess of Wisdom, War, the arts, and crafts -._<br>
